Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:10:00.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk: Grow Glorious Grow edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm Rina Honnizumi, the voice of Momojan's Shizuku Hinomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:09.67,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:22.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,This ProSeka AfterTalk is a place where we look back on the event story and enjoy the AfterLive together with everyone watching the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:27.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,This time, we're covering the Grow Glorious Grow event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:35.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,The event just ended a moment ago, but did you all check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:41.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll be keeping an eye on the comments, so please send them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:48.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Actually, I jotted down some notes earlier about things I wanted to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:54.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,so I'm looking forward to discussing those with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's the plan, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was just so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:06.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Both as Momojan and as Shizuku, she's overcome so many walls, and she'd already grown wings and taken flight, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's still surpassing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,Her growth just doesn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's truly cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:21.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, please post your thoughts on the event and this broadcast using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:25.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,I have the YouTube chat right here in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,so I'll be picking up any comments that catch my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.86,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, Kon-more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:36.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,The staff has provided me with a device again this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:42.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,so I'd like to use it to look at the story and the illustrations of the members appearing in this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:50.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Also, I'll be creating a private room for the AfterLive so we can watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:56.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll share the Room ID around 21:55, and I'll let you know again when the time comes.
Comment: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Story Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:01.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Get your devices ready, let's watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Comment: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Story Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:14.02,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,Now then, let's dive right into the story for this event, Grow Glorious Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:19.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I want to look back on it, but first,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd like to watch a bit with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Just one episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:24.99,Default,host,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,well, opinions might be split.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:29.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,I have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:36.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,But I'm personally thinking I'd like to see Episode 7. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,How about you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please let me know in the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Ah, look, people are already saying 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,You're all so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:52.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, 7 would be good? 7 it is then. Since you're all suggesting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:58.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Then let's watch Episode 7 together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:00.69,Default,host,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm the one who has to start it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:03.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's not "here you go."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,My bad, I'll start it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:09.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-chan is such a good girl, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:40.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,And... that's as far as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:44.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,That was the moment they truly recognized each other as rivals.
Comment: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:49.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,With that said, let's watch Episode 7 together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,That went by so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:51.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,And that's it for the clip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:59.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Actually, I really love the part after this, where everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,When they're all at More More House watching the commercial that actually aired, and we see Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:11.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,I love that part, and I also love seeing Minori-chan getting all pure and excited, screaming with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:12.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:19.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,Um, I have so much I want to say, but we need to start the live show together at 10:55.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:23.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really want to see the live show, so everyone, please keep an eye on the clock too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:23.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:29.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,I might just keep talking without noticing the time... but I really want to chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:32.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think I'll talk for as long as time allows.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:35.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:38.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:48.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,There are a few scenes I like... Let's review some parts that weren't in the episodes we just watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:56.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-san from Rewrite, who was there, previously performed with them at the Idol Lover festival in a past event.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.36,0:23:02.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's a member of a wonderful unit that met Momojan there, and it feels like they'll develop a nice rivalry going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:11.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,And here she is again,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:14.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,appearing as Shizuku's rival while they co-star as models.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:21.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,They're both stepping up their game, and I'm really looking forward to seeing what's next for those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:23.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,Also, regarding Shizuku's past,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:32.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,there were several flashback scenes. I've forgotten exactly which episodes they were in, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:42.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd love for everyone to go back and watch them, but a junior member who greeted Shizuku during her Cheerful＊Days era makes an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:54.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Back then, Shizuku was overwhelmed with work and was being produced as a "mysterious" idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:24:01.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was a really painful time when she was pushing herself so hard. And in the middle of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:06.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,a new junior member joined... She had worked so hard to get in because she admired her seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:11.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,There's a scene where she tells Shizuku directly, "That's why I'm going to do my best too."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:15.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,At that moment, Shizuku... for me, I...
Comment: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:21.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was a time when Shizuku felt she wasn't suited to be the center of Cheerful Days and was feeling really down,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:28.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,but by meeting those juniors, she realized she was carrying their futures on her shoulders too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.70,0:24:35.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,She felt that if she lacked confidence, she had to polish herself until she found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.00,0:24:35.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.88,0:24:39.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,this was another important encounter for her, meeting those juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.44,0:24:47.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,That was a scene that really moved me and that I personally loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:56.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,Also, the Momojan members... After Shizuku passed the audition this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:25:01.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,while she was practicing silently by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.88,0:25:08.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,they brought her some snacks and things. In the card stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.16,0:25:11.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,that sense of distance they have at that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.56,0:25:14.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,is depicted really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.84,0:25:25.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,Airi-chan especially knows Shizuku from her Cheerful Days era so well,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:35.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,so she can feel Shizuku's level of commitment without needing any words. That's why Airi-chan intentionally didn't say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.64,0:25:42.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,and just watched over her. That dynamic within Momojan...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.34,0:25:47.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,it really makes me feel all over again what wonderful girls they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.48,0:25:54.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku was like a string pulled taut the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.28,0:26:12.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,with this intense tension and a sense of fragility, but Airi-chan was happy to see Shizuku looking like she did back when she was the center of Cheerful Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.42,0:26:14.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's just so emotional, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.32,0:26:19.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,But Airi-chan also knows how much Shizuku suffered back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.90,0:26:21.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Of course, she doesn't say that to Shizuku directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.52,0:26:29.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,but she takes all of that into account while watching her grow. That's their relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.56,0:26:34.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really felt like saying "Thank you for writing this"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.10,0:26:37.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,during the recording session.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.32,0:26:43.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Looking at the comments... Yes, everyone, it's all about trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.84,0:26:44.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.76,0:26:51.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Now, about Shizuku's side story, part two.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.44,0:26:53.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's a nice way of giving back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.40,0:27:01.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone was thinking about what they could do for Shizuku and taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.00,0:27:11.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,Since she was being stoic and restricting her diet, they brought her snacks
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.10,0:27:15.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,that were high in nutrition and low in fat. That's just pure love, honestly.
Comment: 0,0:27:15.28,0:27:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.28,0:27:16.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's all about supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.24,0:27:18.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Exactly... Come on, talk a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.12,0:27:20.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.84,0:27:23.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Should we go with the drama?
Comment: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Song Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:29.12,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,So, about that Grand Fleur commercial...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.80,0:27:34.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,What did you all think of the footage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.36,0:27:39.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,that actually aired in the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.02,0:27:45.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,When I record for the game, I usually record my lines alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:57.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,It seems Hagiyama-san had already finished her voice recording, and we had some lines to say in unison.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.40,0:28:03.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,There was a line where Hagiyama-san and Shizuku, along with the others, had to say "Grand Fleur" together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.62,0:28:11.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Normally, for lines in unison, they play the previously recorded voice into my headphones,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.08,0:28:16.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,and I listen to that while recording my part to match the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.98,0:28:24.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's the usual pattern for delivering perfectly synchronized voices to everyone, but get this...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:26.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,We recorded that without matching it to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.52,0:28:29.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,And yet, it was so perfectly in sync!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.84,0:28:37.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was so surprised. I saw the finished version at the same time as all of you, and it was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.92,0:28:45.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,I got an "OK" right away. I thought I might have to redo it, but I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.34,0:28:51.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-chan and Shizuku were just naturally on the same wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:55.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,I can't believe that actually happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:29:01.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,The lines were actually quite long, too, like "The new Floraison Éclat..."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.70,0:29:06.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,I even looked up what kind of color "Floraison Éclat" was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.22,0:29:08.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,It seemed like a really beautiful floral color.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.44,0:29:11.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was just so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:13.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad everyone is saying it's amazing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.23,0:29:14.73,Default,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.44,0:29:19.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,I thought that was a pretty rare occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.88,0:29:28.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,It makes me happy that these two, who met as good rivals, could be so in sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:37.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,I hope they continue to push each other to new heights alongside the other girls from RE:LITE.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.44,0:29:38.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:40.83,Default,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.68,0:29:43.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's talk a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.47,0:29:45.97,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.96,0:30:00.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,Going back to the flashback scenes for a moment... when Shizuku was searching for what she was lacking,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.82,0:30:06.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,MIKU-chan was in Shizuku's room, and Shizuku decided to watch some old footage...
Comment: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:11.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was around the scene where MIKU-chan asks Shizuku-chan how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.70,0:30:20.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,In the scene where they watch footage of Shizuku from her Cheerful Days era, there are lines from the past Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.10,0:30:21.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,"I need to do it more like this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:31.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,We actually recorded several different patterns of her muttering to herself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.80,0:30:32.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.43,0:30:37.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,We delivered one of those versions to all of you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.76,0:30:48.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,For the patterns, there was a version of Shizuku that felt more precarious, like you'd be worried just watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.04,0:31:04.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,She was really pushing herself to the limit, thinking she had to master the dance to carry the weight of being the center of Cheerful Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.28,0:31:11.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,I recorded several takes of that desperate Shizuku. I felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.62,0:31:18.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,We've seen Shizuku backed into a corner like this a few times before,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.74,0:31:23.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,but it's been a while since she went that far. It was actually quite tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.28,0:31:26.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,and there were several scenes that were pretty painful to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.14,0:31:37.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,Flashbacks to the Cheerful Days era always involve lines where she's pushing herself, which can be hard for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.10,0:31:41.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,But that Shizuku is what leads to the Shizuku we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.64,0:31:44.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,I thought having that contrast would create more of a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.47,0:31:46.97,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.32,0:31:49.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:55.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,And yet, a cornered Shizuku has a certain charm of her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.24,0:31:56.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.64,0:32:03.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Especially since she was being promoted as the "mysterious Shizuku" back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.12,0:32:06.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,she never showed that side of her hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.68,0:32:16.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's why seeing her silently working so hard by herself behind the scenes feels so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.72,0:32:20.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Like she was doing her absolute best all on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.12,0:32:25.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's why it connects to the episode with her juniors I mentioned earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.68,0:32:29.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,where Shizuku feels like she has to work hard
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.00,0:32:33.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,for their sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.73,0:32:35.47,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.47,0:32:38.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thinking about it that way, I'm so glad she met Momojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.80,0:32:42.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, Minori...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.80,0:32:43.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Haruka...
Comment: 0,0:32:44.28,0:32:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.28,0:32:45.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's Airi for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.18,0:32:46.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.61,0:32:48.11,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.84,0:32:54.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's about time for me to start getting ready for the AfterLive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.58,0:33:01.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll reveal the Room ID around 10:55, so everyone, please get your devices ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.82,0:33:05.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,We'll do a "ready, set, go" so take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.56,0:33:10.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll try my best not to make any mistakes while setting this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.96,0:33:15.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Okay, creating the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.57,0:33:20.07,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.88,0:33:27.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Writing down the numbers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.72,0:33:28.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.41,0:33:30.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm not showing it yet, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.20,0:33:32.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll show it on the count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.00,0:33:35.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please have your devices ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.88,0:33:38.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,It'll be around 10:55.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.36,0:33:48.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Wait, it won't fit on this, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.61,0:33:50.35,Default,host,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.35,0:33:52.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,This ID has six digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.67,0:34:08.17,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.28,0:34:10.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,I managed to write it down correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:13.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.64,0:34:14.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.84,0:34:19.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,Type it in and enter on my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.54,0:34:23.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Space is limited, so it's first-come, first-served.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.92,0:34:25.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.32,0:34:30.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's all get hyped together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.04,0:34:31.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's the first time everyone's hearing the song, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.76,0:34:33.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.68,0:34:37.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's my first time seeing it too, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.00,0:36:36.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,The AfterLive starts at 22:00.
Comment: 0,0:36:37.80,0:36:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Card Illustrations ===
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.80,0:36:43.38,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,I'm planning to introduce the cards and everything today, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.38,0:36:44.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Just a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.04,0:36:47.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.46,0:36:58.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,The illustration used for Shizuku's banner this time... I was like, "Is this really the untrained version?"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.60,0:37:01.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,The quality is high enough to be a trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:02.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really shocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.56,0:37:07.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,I actually got a sneak peek during the voice recording session,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.72,0:37:10.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,of how Shizuku would look this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.17,0:37:11.67,Default,host,0,0,0,,And man,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.84,0:37:14.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,it was just incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.92,0:37:15.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but applaud.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.82,0:37:16.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.56,0:37:20.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really wish they would sell this actual makeup line.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.46,0:37:23.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.32,0:37:24.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.80,0:37:34.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,We've seen Shizuku looking cool in a few events before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:44.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,the sparkle in her eyes is different here. Her strength and all her hard work really show in her expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.92,0:37:46.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,She looks so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.76,0:37:52.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,The trained illustration is also amazing. It's like she's under a blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.12,0:37:59.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,and you can see her looking like she's about to take flight. Let's all look at the cards together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.84,0:38:01.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,They're wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.56,0:38:02.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,The outfits are cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.92,0:38:06.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's like a hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.60,0:38:09.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,A hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:15.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,The script says it's a studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.88,0:38:18.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.92,0:38:29.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,I thought the set really fit the concept this time. It feels very mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.32,0:38:36.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,But since the goal was to attract a younger audience than Grand Fleur's usual target demographic,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.68,0:38:41.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-chan and Shizuku were selected for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.40,0:38:46.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,They fit the concept so perfectly that it just made me happy.
Comment: 0,0:38:46.68,0:38:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.68,0:38:55.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,ProSeka really does a great job showing so many different sides of the characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.32,0:38:55.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,They really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.52,0:38:59.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Speaking as a fan myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.68,0:39:03.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,seeing such a wide range for the characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.56,0:39:06.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,I bet there were people who literally fell out of their chairs because it was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.68,0:39:07.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.60,0:39:08.57,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.57,0:39:10.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,I mean, you would fall over seeing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.28,0:39:11.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's seriously mind-blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.74,0:39:13.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.60,0:39:18.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,I saw it trending on X earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.16,0:39:22.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,I figured it had to be something about ProSeka.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.20,0:39:26.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,The banner had just been revealed, and I happened to see it right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.74,0:39:34.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,When the official account posted the image for Shizuku's event banner on X,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.94,0:39:37.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,everyone's reactions were just incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.82,0:39:40.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,It made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.12,0:39:43.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,Okay everyone, it's almost time to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.22,0:39:44.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,About ten seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.80,0:39:46.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.06,0:39:47.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.76,0:39:51.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad I get to enjoy this with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.16,0:39:51.71,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.32,0:39:53.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.00,0:47:46.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.04,0:47:50.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, what did you all think?
Comment: 0,0:47:51.28,0:47:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Song Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.28,0:47:57.92,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,Thank you, r-906, for writing "Hashiru" for Momojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.92,0:47:58.63,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's such a great song.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.92,0:48:01.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku says,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.64,0:48:05.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,"Look at me."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.84,0:48:10.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,I've never seen her be this strong before.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.28,0:48:14.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really makes me feel so emotional, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.64,0:48:18.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,In the chorus lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.20,0:48:22.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,it says, "Can you tell who the lead is?"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.92,0:48:26.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,And then, "Look at me."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.16,0:48:34.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,I feel like this really shows... earlier, Shizuku said she'd started leaning on everyone since joining Momojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.48,0:48:38.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's how she described it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.08,0:48:41.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,well, that's definitely not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.76,0:48:48.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was progress in its own way, but she called it "leaning on them."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.12,0:48:51.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,And now, she's climbing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:52.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,to even greater
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.72,0:48:54.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.36,0:49:01.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for writing a song and lyrics that perfectly symbolize that growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.20,0:49:04.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, thank you, r-906.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.84,0:49:05.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.32,0:49:12.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,it's been added to the game now, and I really want you all to pay attention to the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.68,0:49:15.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,How should I put it... wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.92,0:49:19.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,After the first chorus, there's a solo part where,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.90,0:49:21.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,one by one, everyone comes to the center and...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.81,0:49:23.31,Default,host,0,0,0,,well...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.16,0:49:27.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,wasn't that just incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.02,0:49:32.39,Default,host,0,0,0,,The part where Shizuku comes to the center and turns around...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.39,0:49:33.13,Default,host,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.68,0:49:39.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really felt like the formation and the choreography were just god-tier.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.72,0:49:43.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,The lighting, the stage, and the outfits too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.00,0:49:45.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,The outfits were insane.
Comment: 0,0:49:46.76,0:49:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.76,0:49:47.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.38,0:49:51.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,I touched on it a bit with the cards, but you can see a glimpse of it there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.94,0:49:55.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's all pour our love into it together later, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.64,0:49:57.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, thank you so much for all the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.88,0:49:59.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's crying a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.48,0:50:01.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,I totally get that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.78,0:50:02.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.58,0:50:04.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,The outfits were so cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.76,0:50:07.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,They really grab your attention, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.32,0:50:10.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so excited to see what's next
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.56,0:50:14.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,for Momojan, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.02,0:50:14.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.88,0:50:21.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,By the way, the 3DMV was uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:24.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,at 10:10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.44,0:50:26.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.78,0:50:28.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's already live.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.18,0:50:30.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.04,0:50:34.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Since we're here, I'd love for you to watch this broadcast with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.56,0:50:35.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.44,0:50:39.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please watch it a bunch of times later. But if you want to see it right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.60,0:50:40.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,go ahead and watch it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.80,0:50:43.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, I'm so excited for the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.04,0:50:43.69,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.69,0:50:44.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.32,0:50:47.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for the talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.60,0:50:49.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.58,0:50:50.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Being able to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.88,0:50:53.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,deliver a new song to everyone like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.08,0:50:54.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.64,0:50:59.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,there are five members in total who were newly added this time.
Comment: 0,0:50:59.66,0:51:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.66,0:51:03.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, did you check out the side stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.44,0:51:04.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Wait, just a second...
Comment: 0,0:51:05.16,0:51:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Card Illustrations ===
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.16,0:51:06.88,Default,host_meta,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.76,0:51:08.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.96,0:51:10.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.44,0:51:12.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.04,0:51:16.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,The trained version...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.90,0:51:18.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.88,0:51:23.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Isn't the outfit from earlier just incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.92,0:51:26.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, she's truly taking flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.38,0:51:29.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really love the expression on Shizuku's face as she looks back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.38,0:51:31.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think you guys might relate to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.28,0:51:33.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,It shows such strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.96,0:51:35.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.52,0:51:38.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,And this... should I call it a flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.56,0:51:43.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's like a flag... do you see how it's shaped like a wing?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.04,0:51:44.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,On the left side...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.48,0:51:51.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,In the story, there was a metaphor about Shizuku being like a swan...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.76,0:51:52.39,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.32,0:51:54.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,How they look elegant above the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.08,0:51:56.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,...that's how they appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.76,0:52:00.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,but beneath the surface, they're paddling their feet like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.74,0:52:05.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really love that comparison, saying that's exactly what Shizuku is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.78,0:52:09.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,This illustration really captures that feeling perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.24,0:52:11.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.16,0:52:12.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,So gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.36,0:52:15.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Next, here is the untrained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.24,0:52:16.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,The banner art.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.28,0:52:17.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.24,0:52:22.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,This appeared in the story earlier too... it really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.42,0:52:24.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,Look at Shizuku here...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.16,0:52:25.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Isn't she sparkling?
Comment: 0,0:52:27.24,0:52:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.24,0:52:30.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,The level of expression just keeps getting better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.16,0:52:34.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Look at the way Shizuku is holding that poster in her right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.53,0:52:35.03,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.64,0:52:38.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, I want this for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.76,0:52:41.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,It is just too beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.08,0:52:43.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,I could stare at it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.04,0:52:44.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.80,0:52:47.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,Maybe I should use this as a reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.66,0:52:48.35,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.08,0:52:50.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,It is seriously good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.56,0:52:54.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,When it is zoomed in like this... by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.80,0:52:57.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Since she looks so mature, I tried to act a bit more mature myself
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.04,0:52:59.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,while performing her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.50,0:53:04.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,I can't help but be conscious of it when the art is this wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.28,0:53:06.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.96,0:53:07.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,That was Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.93,0:53:09.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,Next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.24,0:53:11.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Minori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.32,0:53:14.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.56,0:53:15.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,She is bursting with energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.94,0:53:18.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I love Minori-chan's jumps. You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.12,0:53:23.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,she is always the one jumping the highest during our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.72,0:53:25.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,She is seriously the personification of Momojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.40,0:53:27.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,That leap...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.08,0:53:30.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Minori-chan's full effort really reaches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.56,0:53:33.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.89,0:53:38.39,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.57,0:53:40.07,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.20,0:53:43.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,This angle is also just irresistible.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.40,0:53:45.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,You can even see her shoes...
Comment: 0,0:53:45.14,0:53:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.14,0:53:46.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,There are wings on the heels of the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.82,0:53:48.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.32,0:53:51.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,The attention to detail is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.20,0:53:52.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,I can really feel the dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.40,0:53:54.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.58,0:53:57.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,The designs are slightly different for each member,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.20,0:53:59.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,so I can't help but stare at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.32,0:54:02.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.08,0:54:04.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Wait, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.60,0:54:08.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,That was Episode 7 just now. Look at what happens after.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.88,0:54:09.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.20,0:54:15.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is when everyone watched the Grand Fleur commercial together,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.24,0:54:18.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,and then this expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.56,0:54:25.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Airi's look here is just... I love this vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.08,0:54:27.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.24,0:54:30.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,Minori, seriously, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.78,0:54:31.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.16,0:54:34.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,And then, there's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.96,0:54:37.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's Momo House.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.00,0:54:41.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen Momo House from this angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.52,0:54:42.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,This illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.50,0:54:43.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,So that's what it looked like!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.60,0:54:47.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so heartwarming. It's Momo House.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.48,0:54:52.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,Moving on... MIKU.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.70,0:54:55.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,You can feel such a strong sense of will
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.88,0:54:57.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,from this MIKU.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.12,0:54:59.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.32,0:55:02.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,MIKU...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.20,0:55:06.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,She shows so many different expressions depending on her resolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.20,0:55:11.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,and it's like she's carrying Shizuku's determination right along with her.
Comment: 0,0:55:11.32,0:55:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.32,0:55:16.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,MIKU also, well, she stayed close to Shizuku in her own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.36,0:55:21.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,and treated her with such a wonderful sense of distance. MIKU supported her,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.16,0:55:25.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,and she was able to overcome it. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.24,0:55:26.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's a goddess, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.44,0:55:27.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.84,0:55:29.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,MIKU is so cool too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.88,0:55:31.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,She looks so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.88,0:55:32.63,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.20,0:55:34.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, cool MIKU is just... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.56,0:55:36.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.52,0:55:37.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.24,0:55:40.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.92,0:55:43.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Miyashitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.04,0:55:45.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,The untrained art...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.80,0:55:46.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.72,0:55:50.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's that one. Not from just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.36,0:55:51.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.20,0:55:57.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's from when I was talking about the Shizuku of the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.00,0:56:02.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,the two of them are watching Shizuku practicing her dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.16,0:56:05.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's MIKU staying close to her while they check the screen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.66,0:56:07.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.16,0:56:08.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Man, this distance between them is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.68,0:56:11.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Watching over her from so close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.36,0:56:15.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,This scene is exactly that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.36,0:56:16.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,From the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.36,0:56:18.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.36,0:56:21.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.52,0:56:25.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,about the Shizuku of the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.88,0:56:28.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,it's the part where she tells her that she's the Shizuku of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.36,0:56:30.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's the spot.
Comment: 0,0:56:30.22,0:56:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.22,0:56:35.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, Shizuku watches footage of her past self and says it doesn't even feel like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.76,0:56:38.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,And this is the scene where MIKU tells her,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.60,0:56:41.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,"This is you too, Shizuku-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.23,0:56:42.73,Default,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.96,0:56:45.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so heartwarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.12,0:56:47.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,You can really feel that she's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.92,0:56:51.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,MIKU is always there to support us, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.20,0:56:52.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.52,0:56:55.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,It makes me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.36,0:56:57.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.52,0:57:02.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,Here's Haruka-chan's trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.40,0:57:06.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's sitting down... this is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.08,0:57:09.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,That look of her watching over Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.48,0:57:12.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.08,0:57:16.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone understands Shizuku so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.12,0:57:17.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Well, they all understand each other, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.24,0:57:22.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Units are just so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.28,0:57:25.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone is there for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.40,0:57:29.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,and because Shizuku is there, everyone else is there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.48,0:57:31.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.41,0:57:32.91,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.56,0:57:35.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,Really, always...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.42,0:57:36.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,I can't stop saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.20,0:57:39.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,This white clover is nice too, the three-leaf one.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.04,0:57:40.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Momojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.92,0:57:46.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,The coloring is slightly different for each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.16,0:57:51.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,This time, it's all unified with a blue sky, as if to cheer on Shizuku as she takes flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.24,0:57:54.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really suits Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.60,0:57:57.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.96,0:58:04.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Personally, I like that Shizuku is wearing short pants... the shorts and...
Comment: 0,0:58:05.48,0:58:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.48,0:58:08.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,The legs are asymmetrical too...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.00,0:58:11.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,And this is what you'd call the "absolute territory."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.44,0:58:13.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.04,0:58:16.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.28,0:58:18.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Shorts really suit Haruka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.20,0:58:20.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,She looks as brilliant as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.04,0:58:24.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Now, for this illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.68,0:58:27.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is the untrained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.34,0:58:28.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Haruka is...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.56,0:58:35.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's making a high-nutrition, low-calorie meal
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.96,0:58:37.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,specifically for Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.44,0:58:38.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.40,0:58:44.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan is so stoic and works so hard on her own diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.24,0:58:45.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.40,0:58:48.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,so of course she's very knowledgeable,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.44,0:58:52.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,she knows so much about nutritional value.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.36,0:58:56.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even I learn things just by looking at the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.11,0:58:57.61,Default,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.28,0:59:00.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Like, "This is a bit high in fat," or,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.28,0:59:07.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,"This is a sweet you can eat even on a low-carb diet."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.44,0:59:12.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm like, "Oh, I see!" and use it as a reference myself sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.84,0:59:17.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Physical health... food is the foundation of your physical health.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.40,0:59:18.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,It starts with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.82,0:59:19.51,Default,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.04,0:59:21.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Building the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.68,0:59:23.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,And that's how Haruka-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.56,0:59:26.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,is supporting Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.76,0:59:28.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.74,0:59:30.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so colorful,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.80,0:59:32.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,it looks great.
Comment: 0,0:59:32.36,0:59:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.36,0:59:33.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.48,0:59:36.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,...Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.32,0:59:41.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,For Airi-chan, we only have the untrained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.08,0:59:42.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.84,0:59:45.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's showing her midriff, which is so typical of Airi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.13,0:59:46.63,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.72,0:59:50.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Airi-chan is just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.00,0:59:51.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,That wink...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.08,0:59:55.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's just bursting with energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.28,0:59:57.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,it really shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.88,0:59:58.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.96,1:00:01.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,When you think of Airi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.46,1:00:02.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,you can't go wrong with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.58,1:00:03.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.52,1:00:05.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.56,1:00:08.34,Default,host,0,0,0,,...this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.34,1:00:11.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was really happy we could look at these together just now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.77,1:00:13.27,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.16,1:00:16.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,And with that,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.04,1:00:20.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,we've managed to see all of them for this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.84,1:00:21.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.68,1:00:25.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Some of you mentioned it in the comments too, but for this event...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.60,1:00:26.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,...?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.88,1:00:27.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,The team name.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.88,1:00:29.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,I made it "Fabulous."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.98,1:00:33.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yes, Fabulous. Honestly, that one word says it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.05,1:00:34.55,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.04,1:00:37.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.80,1:00:39.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.16,1:00:42.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,let me talk a little bit more.
Comment: 0,1:00:42.52,1:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.52,1:00:43.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.68,1:00:47.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,I touched on that, but wait, how far did I get?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.74,1:00:50.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right, I talked about my favorite scenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.64,1:00:55.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,And I mentioned the achievement of their voices syncing up for the Grand Fleur commercial.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.72,1:00:56.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.80,1:00:57.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.52,1:01:03.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,In this story, when Shizuku was working on Grand Fleur,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.88,1:01:04.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,and she wanted to improve...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.80,1:01:08.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,She saw Hagiyama-chan's performance,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.00,1:01:16.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,and seeing her strength made her realize, "This is what I'm missing!"
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.74,1:01:18.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,There was that scene where she finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.44,1:01:26.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,I actually really empathized with Shizuku in that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.22,1:01:32.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,When I'm doing my own work and activities,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.36,1:01:36.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,there are so many times when I'm faced with what I'm lacking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.08,1:01:41.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm aware that I'm missing something, and I run right into that wall,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.98,1:01:46.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,but as for what specifically I should do to grasp that missing piece,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.68,1:01:48.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.64,1:01:49.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,I seriously have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.36,1:01:55.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Honestly, I could probably call this the main challenge of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.04,1:01:59.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm very blessed with my environment, and the people around me
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.80,1:02:04.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,are all such charming, cool, and wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.72,1:02:07.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,Because of that, I see them having things that I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.91,1:02:09.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.93,1:02:10.43,Default,host,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.04,1:02:16.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,They look so radiant, and they possess things I lack.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.36,1:02:20.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,When I'm struggling in those moments,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.00,1:02:30.94,Default,host,0,0,0,,I get this image of myself struggling in the deep sea where I can't see any light or the path ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.94,1:02:32.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's really painful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.00,1:02:35.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's like no matter what I do, it backfires,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.36,1:02:37.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,or I just can't get any results.
Comment: 0,1:02:38.12,1:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.12,1:02:40.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Maybe some of you...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.08,1:02:43.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think there might be some people who feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.47,1:02:45.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.14,1:02:46.86,Default,host,0,0,0,,There are times when things are just incredibly painful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.86,1:02:47.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.52,1:02:50.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,when you finally realize it,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.12,1:02:56.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,you realize, "This... this is what I was looking for."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.72,1:02:59.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,There's a moment where it all clicks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.14,1:03:00.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's strange,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.04,1:03:05.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,but you can only understand it the moment you find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.56,1:03:11.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm not sure if I'm explaining this well.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.84,1:03:16.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for not having the right words, but in my experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.46,1:03:21.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,it's something you only understand once you find that light,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.62,1:03:22.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,and you realize, "This was it."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.68,1:03:26.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,You can never see it while you're still struggling,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.08,1:03:29.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,only the version of you that found it can understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.10,1:03:31.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, if right now...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.16,1:03:34.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.40,1:03:37.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,if there's anyone out there who is struggling right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.36,1:03:42.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,it might be painful at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.72,1:03:45.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,but there will be a moment when that light is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.55,1:03:48.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.14,1:03:48.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.74,1:03:50.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is just my take.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.00,1:03:55.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,I hope for a world where that light is within your reach someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.48,1:03:56.11,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.20,1:04:02.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to convey through this story and through Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.24,1:04:06.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,That was the personal theme I took away from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.80,1:04:10.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, let's both keep doing our best.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.58,1:04:11.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,Through everything.
Comment: 0,1:04:12.56,1:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.56,1:04:16.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Whether it is club activities, work, or job hunting,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.72,1:04:18.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.52,1:04:24.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,I know things can be tough. In times like those, I hope you can use ProSeka's stories
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.08,1:04:27.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,to take a little breather, or listen to lots of our songs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.72,1:04:31.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,It would make me so happy if they could become a source of strength or healing for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.96,1:04:32.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.08,1:04:33.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.36,1:04:38.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,When you lack confidence... well, it was the same for Shizuku. Shizuku,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.87,1:04:39.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.38,1:04:46.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,She was happy to pass the Grand Fleur audition, but she did not know
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.04,1:04:52.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,what she needed to do to have the strength to be worthy of co-starring with Hagiyama.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.60,1:04:54.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Being in that state of not knowing,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.72,1:04:57.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,and then having the actual performance approach... that is terrifying, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.76,1:05:00.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,Knowing that you are lacking something,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.56,1:05:04.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,and having to smash through the wall right in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.60,1:05:05.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,it is just so scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.28,1:05:07.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,That lack of confidence,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.28,1:05:11.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,and that fear... it was one of the scenes I really empathized with.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.12,1:05:12.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.32,1:05:16.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,And then, this part.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.32,1:05:16.95,Default,host,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.20,1:05:22.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,after seeing Hagiyama-chan's performance,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.64,1:05:24.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.68,1:05:28.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,not wanting to lose to anyone, or give in...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.04,1:05:30.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.80,1:05:32.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,she felt that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.60,1:05:38.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,When Hagiyama-chan asked Shizuku what she was thinking during the audition,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.58,1:06:04.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think it was during the fitting... she said she was thinking about giving a performance that would surpass her opponent. That really struck a chord with me. I'm lucky enough to get to take many auditions myself, but I get so nervous that I end up putting a lot of pressure on myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.12,1:06:10.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,And of course, because they are such wonderful works, I start worrying if I'll be the one to...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.70,1:06:17.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,drag the project down, or if I can do it well, or if I'll be a burden to my co-stars.
Comment: 0,1:06:17.38,1:06:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.38,1:06:18.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,There are so many different feelings involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.78,1:06:26.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,Sometimes you feel like you're going to be crushed by your own thoughts, but in those moments,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.02,1:06:32.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,if you have that feeling of not wanting to lose or back down, you can hold onto yourself more strongly.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.48,1:06:35.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-chan is seriously so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.54,1:06:36.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.36,1:06:39.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,I ended up learning a lot from her too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.20,1:06:40.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Just like Shizuku did.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.44,1:06:41.19,Default,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.92,1:06:49.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,When someone has a heart that strong, I feel like I'm about to grow wings myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.20,1:06:50.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Like I'm ready to take flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.24,1:06:52.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll do my best right alongside Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.54,1:06:54.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.08,1:06:56.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.96,1:06:58.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,I learn so much from this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.06,1:07:00.82,Default,host,0,0,0,,The stories in ProSeka are just, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.82,1:07:02.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,They're so educational for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.44,1:07:06.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,They've become a source of emotional support.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.84,1:07:14.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd be so happy if they resonate with all of you in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.14,1:07:14.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.64,1:07:18.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone is telling me "Let's do our best!"
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.20,1:07:20.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's do it together, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.92,1:07:22.05,Default,host,0,0,0,,Supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.05,1:07:22.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.56,1:07:23.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for the support.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.26,1:07:24.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.76,1:07:25.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.12,1:07:29.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,My heart is right there with Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.20,1:07:29.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.16,1:07:34.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,With that, I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.00,1:07:37.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,I made sure to memo everything I wanted to talk about, and I've said it all.
Comment: 0,1:07:37.66,1:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.66,1:07:38.19,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.76,1:07:40.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.88,1:07:43.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for staying with me for so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.00,1:07:49.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,The 3DMV for "Hashiru, Todoku" that we just watched together has been released, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.58,1:07:50.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.72,1:07:51.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.92,1:07:53.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Was it 2D?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.88,1:07:59.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,The 2DMV was just uploaded to the official YouTube channel, so please watch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.78,1:08:00.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,It was the 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.80,1:08:01.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.56,1:08:03.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I appreciate your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.60,1:08:11.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,Both the 2DMV and the 3DMV... let me summarize.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.46,1:08:23.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Both the 3DMV and 2DMV for "Hashiru, Todoku" have just been released on the official YouTube channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.80,1:08:28.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Sorry, I always get a bit flustered, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.56,1:08:30.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.58,1:08:34.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Once this is over, please go and watch them a lot, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.92,1:08:36.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.18,1:08:37.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.14,1:08:38.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.88,1:08:40.18,Default,host,0,0,0,,Everyone is saying they'll watch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.18,1:08:41.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.54,1:08:52.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,And with that, this short ProSeka AfterTalk for the "Glow Glorious Glow" event has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.74,1:08:55.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,To everyone watching the stream, how did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.40,1:09:01.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy because everyone's comments were so supportive.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.96,1:09:04.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Momojan is truly the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.52,1:09:08.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,They just keep on growing and growing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.50,1:09:13.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Growth with no ceiling is truly dazzling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.68,1:09:18.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.40,1:09:19.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,I had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.28,1:09:20.64,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really did.
Comment: 0,1:09:21.48,1:09:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.48,1:09:26.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,And that's it for today's look at Grow Glorious Grow... that's a mouthful.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.38,1:09:38.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,If you haven't finished reading Grow Glorious Grow yet, you'll be able to read the full event story from the archives once the next event starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.22,1:09:40.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,So please, read it as many times as you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.72,1:09:47.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,The scenes I mentioned earlier that we didn't get to watch together today are all in there too,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.46,1:09:48.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,so definitely check them out.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.14,1:09:51.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd be so happy if you're reading and think, "Oh, Hon-chan mentioned this part!"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.32,1:09:53.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.56,1:09:59.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,And with that, thank you all for sticking with me for so long today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.42,1:10:01.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll see you again soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.24,1:10:02.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
